message.text:
𝐅𝐀𝐔𝐒𝐓𝐈𝐍𝐎 “𝐁𝐎𝐉𝐈𝐄” 𝐃𝐘 𝐓𝐀𝐊𝐄𝐒 𝐎𝐀𝐓𝐇 𝐀𝐒 𝐍𝐄𝐖 𝐇𝐎𝐔𝐒𝐄 𝐒𝐏𝐄𝐀𝐊𝐄𝐑 🔔

Faustino “Bojie” Dy III, the newly elected representative of Isabela’s 6th District, has officially taken his oath on Wednesday, September 17, 2025, as the new Speaker of the 20th Congress.

Dy garnered 253 votes from members of the House of Representatives, succeeding Leyte 1st District Representative Martin Romualdez.

Laging tandaan, ang TAM na boto, dapat TAMang Boto!
#TAMangBoto

message.text:
𝐅𝐀𝐔𝐒𝐓𝐈𝐍𝐎 “𝐁𝐎𝐉𝐈𝐄” 𝐃𝐘 𝐓𝐀𝐊𝐄𝐒 𝐎𝐀𝐓𝐇 𝐀𝐒 𝐍𝐄𝐖 𝐇𝐎𝐔𝐒𝐄 𝐒𝐏𝐄𝐀𝐊𝐄𝐑 🔔

Faustino “Bojie” Dy III, the newly elected representative of Isabela’s 6th District, has officially taken his oath on Wednesday, September 17, 2025, as the new Speaker of the 20th Congress.

Dy garnered 253 votes from members of the House of Representatives, succeeding Leyte 1st District Representative Martin Romualdez.

Laging tandaan, ang TAM na boto, dapat TAMang Boto!
#TAMangBoto

message.text:
𝐅𝐀𝐔𝐒𝐓𝐈𝐍𝐎 “𝐁𝐎𝐉𝐈𝐄” 𝐃𝐘 𝐓𝐀𝐊𝐄𝐒 𝐎𝐀𝐓𝐇 𝐀𝐒 𝐍𝐄𝐖 𝐇𝐎𝐔𝐒𝐄 𝐒𝐏𝐄𝐀𝐊𝐄𝐑 🔔

Faustino “Bojie” Dy III, the newly elected representative of Isabela’s 6th District, has officially taken his oath on Wednesday, September 17, 2025, as the new Speaker of the 20th Congress.

Dy garnered 253 votes from members of the House of Representatives, succeeding Leyte 1st District Representative Martin Romualdez.

Laging tandaan, ang TAM na boto, dapat TAMang Boto!
#TAMangBoto

Nanlalamig ba kayo dahil sa panahon... o baka naman nanlalamig na kayo ng jowa mo? 👀

Tara! Samahan niyo kami bukas sa Freedom park mula 2PM hanggang 5PM para sa aming busking session. Paiinitin natin ang nanlalamig ninyong mga puso. Umulan man o bumagyo, tuloy parin tayo!

Nanlalamig ba kayo dahil sa panahon... o baka naman nanlalamig na kayo ng jowa mo? 👀

Tara! Samahan niyo kami bukas sa Freedom park mula 2PM hanggang 5PM para sa aming busking session. Paiinitin natin ang nanlalamig ninyong mga puso. Umulan man o bumagyo, tuloy parin tayo!

#OFMR
#OneFeuMusicAndRecords
#BuskingSession
#BuhayAngMusikaSaPiyu
